To run this 200 kb test:

 1. Install and compile ALLPATHS-LG:

      tar xf allpathslg-<revision>.tar.gz

      cd allpathslg-<revision>

      ./configure --prefix=/path/to/install/directory/

      make

      make install


 2. Make sure your PATH includes '/path/to/install/directory/bin/'.


 3. Make sure you stacksize is 100 MB:

      limit stacksize 100000    # on csh

      ulimit -s 100000          # on sh      


 4. Run 'prepare.sh' to generate the ALLPATHS-LG input files.


 5. Run 'assemble.sh' to assemble the data.

